For building nodeJS project we need nodeJS tool just like we need maven build tool for java project.
# yum install nodejs -y

To create package 
# npm install

When we built a nodeJS project for the very first time. It will downloaded all dependencies from nodjs central repository or remote repository.
It will create one folder called as node_module and store all downloaded dependancies in it.

To execute sonarqube report
# npm run sonar OR # node sonar-project.js

Java - Maven Build Tool               Node Js
----------------------                ------- 
pom.xml                               package.json (Node Modules)

mvn clean package                     npm install

mvn clean sonar:sonar                 npm run sonar (OR) node sonar-project.js

pom.xml                               sonar-project.js

mvn deploy                            npm publish

pom.xml --> nexus repos               package.json --> nexus repos

settings.xml --> nexus credentilas    Create file .npmrc --> nexus credentials -- base64 
